      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:22:7",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/22/217",
      "text": [
        " «لاَ بَأْسَ بِأَنْ يَتَيَمَّمَ وَ لاَ يَغْتَسِلَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.217 - Muhammad ibn Muslim asked Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) about a man who has sores and wounds and becomes junub (ritually impure due to sexual discharge).\nImam (as) said: 'There is no harm if he performs tayammum and does not make ghusl (ritual bath).'"
        ]
      }
    },
